<GUIClass name="MB_HHMsgBoxForm" id="a859b52f-719e-4edc-8b57-2effbec6c4eb">
    <superclass name="MB_BaseFormModal"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Description:

This form is a juiced emulation of the form which app.msgBox displays.

It is used by calling the app.displayDialog method, which takes the same parameters
as app.msgBox, and returns the same values.

Notes:

	1. MsgBox_System_Modal is ignored. All calls are treated as MsgBox_App_Modal.

	2. The captions on the buttons are set from translatable strings (of the form
		$MsgBox_Caption_...), which may include an '&amp;' character to specify an accelerator
		key. When translating for another locale, ensure that these accelerator key
		specifications are consistent and the captions are short enough to fit in the
		buttons when displayed in bold font.</text>
